    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed required levels. The single below-threshold factor (Test conditions, achieved level 2 vs. required level 3) is accepted as a residual gap given that the COU is limited to quasi-static compression-bending and the regulatory decision consequence is Medium. E/uval < 1.96 and percent difference < 10% for all three QoIs across N=11 constructs and two laboratories. The FEA modeling framework is judged credible for the stated COU. Note: this package conforms to ProfileMinimal; the signature workflow is pending and will be completed prior to regulatory submission.",
